{"tid":2093072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國下周五解除對港澳台等旅客入境英格蘭後需檢疫措施","createTime":"2020-07-03T15:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:17:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b82f81e3bd09e54737d03501d99ccb451587cda5","tid":2093072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535696-20200703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535696-20200703.htm&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9d993567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535696-20200703.htm&h=e2e14c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535696-20200703.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府宣布，由7月10日起，來自59個國家或地區的旅客，入境英格蘭時毋須再檢疫14日。<br />\n<br />\n被列入名單的包括港澳台、澳紐、法國、德國、意大利、日本、荷蘭、南韓、西班牙、越南等。<br />\n<br />\n美國、加拿大及葡萄牙未被列入名單之上，意味來自這些國家的旅客，入境英格蘭後仍然要自我隔離14日。"},{"pid":"4b546260e3857c378166502d0841fe6b31bc551b","tid":2093072,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"簡化著草程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8971c4d8e52f049376b467424d8ffcfdef42c60","tid":2093072,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d32c608b791a8886a333210b2c0a2d4fcfaf3e","tid":2093072,"uid":124711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"Th